<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>5: It’s only 1 group of 5.</li>
      <li>10: I added 5 more on to the first answer.</li>
      <li>15: I added <m>5+5+5</m>.</li>
      <li>20: I counted by 5.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


